ger for \u00e5 m\u00f8te det, for eksempel \u00e5 selge sofaen.", "- Ikke alle g\u00e5r s\u00e5 drastisk til verks. Har du andre r\u00e5d til de som \u00f8nsker \u00e5 komme seg opp av sofaen i p\u00e5sken?", "- Litt er bedre enn ingenting. Man kan for eksempel gj\u00f8re litt i hagen eller g\u00e5 en liten tur, sier B\u00f8."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "sport"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "sport|sprek"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "e2e772526e924181b71abbc43670a5511962ad743f9337775aaf88847e438334"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-01T15:46:42.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Anette B\u00f8en mener sofaen er s\u00e5 god \u00e5 sitte i at det tar livet av mannen hennes."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article10808334.ece/b5yviy/ALTERNATES/w980-default/SOFA-542.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/237642ab3cbb88d77bff48e4d8e5c05ca9b28cf3.jpg?59075862"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["\u00abLivsfarlig sofa selges\u00bb -adressa.no", "- Kan ikke leve p\u00e5 sofaen", "Morsomt stunt"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "237642ab3cbb88d77bff48e4d8e5c05ca9b28cf3"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim", "ukeadressa", "eadressa", "skattelister", "d\u00f8dsfall", "tr\u00f8nder", "trafikk"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "nyheter,trondheim,ukeadressa,eadressa,skattelister,d\u00f8dsfall,tr\u00f8nder,trafikk"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["sport", "sprek"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "hobbies-and-interests"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "facebook"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["annonsen", "sofa", "fysisk aktivitet", "sofa selges"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["helsedirektoratet", "finn"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "va